Veteran Nollywood actress, who has been heartbroken since the demise of her daughter of over 30 years, has finally found joy again in arms of a new love interest. The actress lost her only child, Aladi Godgift Ameh, whom she bore at 14 to death on October 20, 2020, following an unsuccessful surgery in Abuja. However, it seems joy has finally found her again as the 47-year-old actress took to her social media handle to share a cute photo of herself and new lover whom she publicly appreciated and declared her love for. Sharing their loving photo via her Instagram page, the actress captioned the post: ”I Love you!! Thank you for everything you do for me.” Meanwhile her colleagues in the movie industry as well as fans have wished her unending joy with her new found love.